reviewText:
The game is awesome, maybe Medici has a little bit more boring environment in comparison to Panau from JC2. But I really like new RicoÂ´s skills. What's the biggest dissapointment for me? The optimalization .. FPS drops and stutter, I can't really enjoy the game at 100%. I'll update my review as it gets patched.

//26.December 2015 - Nvidia patch
I am able to play on my notebook with GTX860M even on high settings. But I feel more comfortable playing on desktop with AMD gpu, so my negative review remains. The game itself is nice.
